description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'Girl Power Row' from the channel Sera Moon Busse.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor rowing.
It's suitable for Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe.
The The Warrior Workout vibe means Unleash your inner beast. Sweat-dripping, heart-pounding, primal energy. This is especially good for Days when you want to destroy stress and feel invincible. The The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe means Beat-driven, strong but fluid, music-infused. This is especially good for When you want strength and rhythm to blend seamlessly..
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging and Extreme.

Original workout description: Pay tribute to the powerful women with Sera Moon as you tackle 1- minute intervals. 

Max rhythm: 32, Format: HIIT...
